{"id":420,"date":"2008-06-13T09:58:34","date_gmt":"2008-06-13T01:58:34","guid":{"rendered":"http://xbeta.info/?p=420"},"modified":"2008-06-13T09:58:34","modified_gmt":"2008-06-13T01:58:34","slug":"evernote-d","status":"publish","link":"https://xbeta.info/evernote-d.htm","title":{"rendered":"手工压缩EverNote数据库"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft\" style=\"float: left;\" src=\"http://preview.evernote.com/images/enlogo-beta.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"246\" height=\"50\" /><em>EverNote 可以处理大数据库（似乎记得异尘行者的数据库有200+MB），但也不妨手工压缩一下。网友 Tom Lee 发来邮件如下：</em></p>\n<p>您好，我是firefox和evernote的忠实用户<br />\n前两天在你的网站上面看到了关于evernote 3数据库压缩的问题<br />\n本人也是数据量过大，经常整理，但是数据库最后还是太大<br />\n昨天无意之间看到了evernote 3的about<br />\n发现下面一句话：<strong>SQLite database engine</strong></p>\n<p>也就是说evernote 3用的是sqlite的数据库来存放数据<br />\n曾经我的firefox配置文件夹里面的places</p>\n<div id=\"1ep0\" class=\"ArwC7c ckChnd\">.sqlite也达到过10M<br />\n删除历史记录等后经过下面方法压缩了一下，恢复到了400k<br />\n经试验对evernote有效，望通过您与大家分享<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">（试验前请先备份，本人机器上可用，但是不保证所有人机器上都可用）</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">（本操作针对evernote 3）</span></span><br />\n一、下载安装SQLite Developer（我这里是2.8.8.277，sqlite dll版本是3.5.9）<br />\n二、在左边的&#8221;数据库列表&#8221;上面点右键选&#8221;注册数据库&#8221;，起别名并定位到数据文件<br />\n三、双击打开数据库，然后在数据库上面点右键选&#8221;压缩数据库&#8221;<br />\n四、在数据库上面点右键选&#8221;注销数据库&#8221;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">PS：本人数据文件原为35M，经过压缩，缩小到30M</span></span></p>\n</div>\n<p>></iframe></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>EverNote 可以处理大数据库（似乎记得异尘行者的数据库有200+MB），但也不妨手工压缩一下。网友 To [&hellip;]</p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":["1 文本办公","1.4 信息管理","未分类"],"tags":["Evernote","all"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/420"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/users/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/comments?post=420"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/420/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/media?parent=420"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/categories?post=420"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/tags?post=420"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https://api.w.org/{rel}","templated":true}]},"wp_type":"post"}